---
// WelcomeCard.astro
---
<div class="welcome-card">
    <h2>Selamat Datang Kembali!</h2>
    <p>Pantau status transaksi top up game, pulsa, dan pesanan digital Anda secara real-time di bawah ini.</p>
</div>

<style>
    .welcome-card {
        background: #e8f4fd;
        border: 2px solid #b8daff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .welcome-card h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #004085;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .welcome-card p {
        color: #004085;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0;
    }
</style>
